content: odilitime: Merged two significant PRs this week: #3509 moving characters to a submodule (-6792/+1655 lines) and #3429 introducing a v1 CLI utility, demonstrating a focus on codebase restructuring and feature development. Made substantial code changes across 2607 files (-380769/+31286 lines) primarily in configuration and documentation areas, while also providing 18 code reviews (12 approvals) and contributing 28 comments across PRs and issues.
